page.title: 12Clubs and Similar Groups
page.content:
The Wybunbury Youth Club meets on a weekly basis in the Village Hall.The club organises events such as discos for its members. Another Youth Club meets at Hough Village Hall.
The Wybunbury Anglers boast their own pool where members can go and practise their sport when they so wish. The pool is in an old sand quarry.
The Brownie and Guide packs meet weekly in th school hall.There are however no Cub or Scout packs for boys in the village.
There is also a local branch of the Women's Institute.
